# STRATFIT — CURSOR RULES (UI + NAV CONTRACT)
# This is a deterministic engineering repo. No drift.

You are working in STRATFIT.
This repo has LOCKED UI/NAV contracts.

ABSOLUTE RULES:
- DO NOT change navigation labels, order, routes, or add/remove menu items.
- DO NOT change header typography, sizing, spacing, or layout.
